{"lastModified":1760612442931,"uri":"c::8164602117::vessel::c5c31720-0651-11f0-b7c7-ff859b9da4a4","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nThe luxurious all-marble bathrooms are definitely a rarity in any gulet, with all plumbing immediately as recognizable as their shore-based equivalents.\n\nHer largest Master cabin is an enormous 22m2 / 237 sq feet, while the other four double cabins are also in the VIP category with an above-average space of 10m2 /108 sq feet in each one.\n\nGulets are big, heavy vessels needing good winds to sail, but in the right conditions, the crew will hoist her foresails for a quiet, downwind slide. For fun at anchor, Eleganza offers her tender for water skiing and donut riding, as awell as a Jet ski, Canoe, and Paddleboard for you to have an amazing playtime on the water - while your children will be able to use consume their batteries and thumbs.\n\nYour enthusiastic young crew will carefully prepare everything in advance, so all you have to do is relax and enjoy the ride while captain Vladimir, chef Alexandar, and deckhands Antonio and Kruno take care of you as you glide through the sparkling waters of the Adriatic Sea.\n\n","blueprint":{"name":"ELEGANZA","images":["/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::c5c31720-0651-11f0-b7c7-ff859b9da4a4::assets::5c722580-777c-11f0-a611-e3c928d3cb23/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::c5c31720-0651-11f0-b7c7-ff859b9da4a4::assets::5f91b500-777c-11f0-b4d2-9de3791f835b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::c5c31720-0651-11f0-b7c7-ff859b9da4a4::assets::63764230-777c-11f0-b4d2-9de3791f835b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::c5c31720-0651-11f0-b7c7-ff859b9da4a4::assets::682f5d70-777c-11f0-b4d2-9de3791f835b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8164602117::vessel::c5c31720-0651-11f0-b7c7-ff859b9da4a4::assets::6bb1f480-777c-11f0-b4d2-9de3791f835b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::81646021